Ranger Help for: reconnoiter
=============================

SYNTAX:      recon <direction>
             reconnoiter <direction>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     40
SKILL TYPE:  cartography

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to scout an adjacent room without entering
it, revealing information about what lies in that direction. The scout
report includes creatures present, other players, notable items, and
the terrain type. The amount of detail depends on the Ranger's skill
level and perception. Reconnoiter is useful for planning routes and
avoiding dangerous encounters. The alias 'recon' can be used for speed.
